breeds.name: Gomez

temperment.family: Good with kids
temperment.social: Not friendly with other dogs

breeds.description: Gomez is the perfect dog for a lazy day. He is loving toward a few, but will bite if you try and make him walk in the rain

breeds.name: Shae

temperment.family: Good for an active family
